WEBVTT

00:02.957 --> 00:05.423
Is Georgie mine?

00:05.424 --> 00:08.156
Of course Georgie is yours!
He's our little boy!

00:08.157 --> 00:10.423
James isn't Georgie's father.

00:10.424 --> 00:12.623
- But you said...
- I didn't give birth to him.

00:12.624 --> 00:16.590
You be as cavalier as you
wish with your marriage,

00:16.591 --> 00:18.989
but not with Georgie.

00:18.990 --> 00:20.423
He is a Bligh.

00:20.424 --> 00:22.223
He will be raised by us.

00:22.224 --> 00:25.123
Bear all the shame and part with my son?

00:25.124 --> 00:28.323
That is truly a Bligh solution.

00:28.324 --> 00:29.391
So what now?

00:29.957 --> 00:31.690
The truth.

00:31.691 --> 00:35.089
There's just one little thing
I need you to do for me.

00:35.090 --> 00:36.356
Could you teach me Italian?

00:36.357 --> 00:37.956
I could pay you.

00:37.957 --> 00:39.989
He's taught me a few words already.

00:39.990 --> 00:42.556
You'll be quite the Italiana
before you're done.

00:42.557 --> 00:44.523
You're not interested
in what I've written.

00:44.524 --> 00:47.323
Your subject matter, no.

00:47.324 --> 00:49.490
Perhaps Sir Richard might
advise on the way forward.

00:49.491 --> 00:52.757
No. Anna would rather
succeed on her own merits.

00:52.758 --> 00:53.790
Give me a kiss.

00:53.791 --> 00:57.557
He forced himself on me.

00:58.090 --> 00:59.390
He won't get away with this.

00:59.391 --> 01:02.289
I think your mother was
wrong about Sir Richard.

01:02.290 --> 01:04.989
Will you fetch me my book?
It's in my top drawer there.

01:04.989 --> 01:07.956
Whatever was between us,
George, you're a married man.

01:07.957 --> 01:10.523
- Nothing else matters.
- I'm equally unavailable.

01:10.524 --> 01:12.289
We will be together, Sarah.

01:12.290 --> 01:13.989
For one so young
to take her life.

01:13.990 --> 01:14.956
And then to use...

01:14.957 --> 01:16.490
If it hadn't been your mixture,

01:16.491 --> 01:17.790
she would have used something else.

01:17.791 --> 01:19.591
If she killed herself.

01:20.524 --> 01:22.289
What if she didn't?

01:22.290 --> 01:24.156
Your husband shot George Bligh.

01:24.157 --> 01:26.223
- I don't see what that...
- It's all right, Jack.

01:26.224 --> 01:27.690
I hear you're a Communist, too.

01:27.691 --> 01:31.390
The new Mrs. Bligh and I have
formed a delightful intimacy.

01:31.391 --> 01:34.723
Imagine my thrill the other
day when she visited me

01:34.724 --> 01:37.391
and even stayed to help
me with my little tasks.

01:43.824 --> 01:46.390
To what do I owe this displeasure?

01:46.391 --> 01:49.156
How does it feel to be a murderer?

01:50.006 --> 01:53.904
